# BRAINFUCK PROGRAMS COLLECTION
# Programs run sequentially on a shared tape.
# Hello World uses cells 0-6 (ends at dp=6).
# Programs 2-4 use cells 10-11 (fresh area).

# PROGRAM 1 - Hello, World!
++++++++[>++++[>++>+++>+++>+<<<<-]>+>+>->>+[<]<-]>>.>---.+++++++..+++.>>.<-.<.+++.------.--------.>>+.>++.

# Move to cell 10 (4 steps right from end position dp=6)
>>>>

# PROGRAM 2 - Alphabet A to Z
# cell10=count(26), cell11=char(65=A)
>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<++++++++++++++++++++++++++[>.+<-]>[-]<[-]
++++++++++.[-]

# PROGRAM 3 - Count 1 to 9
# cell10=count(9), cell11=digit(49=1)
>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<+++++++++[>.+<-]>[-]<[-]
++++++++++.[-]

# PROGRAM 4 - Fibonacci sequence: 1 1 2 3 5 8
# Direct ASCII output at cell10, no loops
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++.[-]
++++++++++.[-]
